Turn on scriptblock log
https://learn.microsoft.com/ja-jp/powershell/module/microsoft.powershell.core/about/about_logging_windows?view=powershell-7.5#enabling-scriptblock-logging

```powershell
function Enable-PSScriptBlockLogging {
    $basePath = @(
        'HKLM:\Software\Policies\Microsoft'
        'PowerShellCore\ScriptBlockLogging'
    ) -join '\'

if (-not (Test-Path $basePath)) {
        $null = New-Item $basePath -Force
    }

Set-ItemProperty $basePath -Name EnableScriptBlockLogging -Value "1"
}
```
